        <a name='S5LV0636P0_20020618_GCR_171'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gareth-williams' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020618_GCR_171' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gareth Williams' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gareth-williams" title="Mr Gareth Williams">Lord Williams of Mostyn</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This may be a convenient moment for us to adjourn before we re-congregate tomorrow at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0636P0-02718'>
        <a name='S5LV0636P0_20020618_GCR_172'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-geoffrey-russell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020618_GCR_172' title='Link to this speech by Mr Geoffrey Russell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-geoffrey-russell" title="Mr Geoffrey Russell">The Deputy Chairman of Committees (Lord Ampthill)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Wednesday 19th June at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0636P0-02719'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020618_GCR_173' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at half-past six o'clock.
      </p>
